{"tid":1130183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"四圍求救 中左cwb legend fight and fitness伏","createTime":"2019-04-29T00:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T14:08:00.000Z","uid":115397,"like":3,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0a59f3cad34193b0bcb01db66a34c37b00343c86","tid":1130183,"uid":115397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T00:47:59.000Z","msg":"自責左先，自己係on9。人哋話想收工得番一張卡要挀，就叫我求其寫啲野再上去，結果就好心想幫佢就on99上左去。<br />\n<br />\n上到去知出左事又唔識拒絕人，結果比人水左，店員開始就話未必買到package我本身都表明左唔想買但係就驚佢哋軟硬兼施，結果簽左係個iPad到，彈左code又話一定要報，見我真係無錢就改個平啲嘅plan，但就cancel 唔到比左12k佢，跟著又話要報埋私人班又比左1.6k佢先之後等有錢再比。比左啲個人資料佢又簽左約。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下仲有無得救，或者用冷靜期cancel份約錢就凍過水都預左，只係想快啲了結件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人可以入黎救救我呀，各位巴打大神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都聽講話少少方法<br />\n用合約冷靜期<br />\n搵消委會 想攞返錢的話<br />\n搵區議員<br />\n<br />\n有無成功例子可以講講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73335a1f41bef7a6e9246238b17247c4c71be5a7","tid":1130183,"uid":115397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T00:55:33.000Z","msg":"大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86a4b4488188639cc036efcd311322ae845ce31","tid":1130183,"uid":22564,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T00:58:29.000Z","msg":"你一定係油頭毒撚 比mk妹嗲兩句乜都得"},{"pid":"bf09849adc3481774aa2a8dadffe7626a2c0ca36","tid":1130183,"uid":115397,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"b86a4b4488188639cc036efcd311322ae845ce31","tid":1130183,"uid":22564,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T00:58:29.000Z","msg":"你一定係油頭毒撚 比mk妹嗲兩句乜都得"},"citedBy":0,"rep